<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Twitter Sentiment Analyzer</h1>
  <p>Enter the user's name from a twitter account (e.g. @BarackObama), or a Hashtag (e.g. #Football) or a any simple string (e.g. 'Batman Movie'), that you want us to analyze the sentiment through data mining.</p>

  <%= form_tag analyze_path, :class => 'form-inline', :role => 'form' do %>
    <div class="form-group">
    	<%= text_field_tag :search, nil, :class => 'form-control input-lg', :placeholder => '@BarackObama' %>
  	</div>
    <button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" type="submit">Enter</button>
  <% end %>
  </div>
</div>